title: U.S. Auto Parts: 1Q Earnings Snapshot
text:
CARSON, Calif. (AP) _ U.S. Auto Parts Network Inc. (PRTS) on Tuesday reported first-quarter net income of $735,000.
The Carson, California-based company said it had profit of 2 cents per share.
The online auto parts retailer posted revenue of $78.4 million in the period.
In the final minutes of trading on Tuesday, the company's shares hit $2. A year ago, they were trading at $3.61.
